{
  "chapter": 22,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十二回「梅花又现」：饭堂中，孙老先生与辫子姑娘暗示阿飞去救李寻欢，林仙儿则劝阻阿飞不要冒险。阿飞答应不去少林，但暗下决心假冒梅花盗为李寻欢洗刷罪名。林仙儿透露张胜奇为不义之人，阿飞随即出手以梅花盗之名杀死张胜奇。消息传到少林，心湖大师犹豫是否冤枉了李寻欢，心宠却坚称这是李寻欢同党的诡计。一茵一尘送膳时，李寻欢以傲骨姿态索要菜单，心湖大师为保五师弟心眉而照办。阿飞在林仙儿陪同下前往申老三的高墙大院，准备第二次出手。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "爷爷，你老人家看那李探花是不是被枉的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "我就算知道他是冤枉的，又有什么用？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "但他的朋友呢？难道也没有一个人肯去救他？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "他若被困在别的地方，也许还有人会去救他，但他被困在少林寺，天下只怕没有一个人能救得了他……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "那么……那么这样一位大英雄，难道就要被活活困死不成？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "法子倒是有一个，只不过希望很渺茫而已。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "什么法子？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "除非那真的梅花盗若是还没有死，又忽然出现了，自然就可证明李寻欢并不是梅花盗，他若非梅花盗，自然也就没有害死心眉大师的理由了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这希望实在渺茫得很，那真的梅花盗就算没有死，也一定早就躲起来了，好教李寻欢做他的替死鬼。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "你的面吃光了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我本来饿得很，可是听了这件事，再也吃不下了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "吃不下就走吧，反正我们就算在这里坐一辈子，也救不了李探花的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你若一直坐在这里，又怎能救得了他？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你看这一老一少两个人是什么来路？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "什么来路？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "这老头子目中神光充足，显然内功不弱，那小姑娘脚步轻灵，动作灵快，轻功也绝不会在我之下。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "依我看，这两人绝不会是走江湖，说大书的，必定另有图谋。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "什么图谋？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "他故意将这件事说给你听，说不定就是要你去送死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "送死？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你既知道李寻欢被困在少林，自然就会不顾一切赶去救他，但你一个人去怎会是少林寺八百弟子的对手？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "何况，他们说的也许全都是假话，为的就是要你去上当。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "就算他们说的不假，李寻欢现在也不会有什么危险，你若去了，反而会令他分心，少林弟子若是以你来要挟他，他也一定会不顾一切出来救你的，那么你非但不是去救他，反而是去害他了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "不错，你考虑得的确比我周到。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你答应我绝不去少林寺冒险？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我既然不去少林寺了，你还是回去吧。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我……我想到别处去走走。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你莫非想去假冒梅花盗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你已打定了主意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "那么……你为什么还要叫我回去？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "这是我自己的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你的事，就是我的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "但李寻欢并不是你的朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你的朋友，就是我的朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你对朋友既然如此够义气，我为什么就不能呢？我虽然没有什么用，可是，两个人在一起，遇到事至少总可以商量商量，总比一个人好。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你若要假冒梅花盗，就得去找几个对象下手才是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我们总不能去找无辜的人，是吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我要找的对象，自然是那些为富不仁的恶霸，坐地分赃的强盗。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我听说，附近就有这么样的一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "此人早年是个绿林巨盗，五十岁以后才金盆洗手，但暗中还是做些不清不白的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你可知道他的名字？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "听说他本来是叫张胜奇，现在却叫张员外，张大善人了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "大善人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "他抢了十万两银子，就用一百两去修桥铺路，晚上杀了一百个人，白天却来施粥赠药……一个强盗若是想做善人，比任何人都容易多了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_sheng_qi",
      "speaker_name": "张胜奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今年春天来得好早……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_sheng_qi",
      "speaker_name": "张胜奇",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "好个不开眼的小贼，竟敢来太岁头上动土！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_jing",
      "speaker_name": "萧静",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "text": "弟子萧静，特来有要事禀报。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_jing",
      "speaker_name": "萧静",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "text": "江湖传说梅花盗又出现了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_jing",
      "text": "梅花盗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "百晓生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_jing",
      "text": "梅花盗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_jing",
      "speaker_name": "萧静",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "text": "三天之前，久已洗手归隐的独行盗张胜奇忽然被杀，家里的珍宝也被洗劫一空，致命的伤痕是五点血迹，状如梅花。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "梅花盗既然又再度出现，李寻欢说的那番话也许就不是假的，也许是我们冤枉了他。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "text": "也许这反而更证明了李寻欢就是梅花盗！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "此话怎讲？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "text": "我若是梅花盗，知道已有人做了我的替死鬼，一定会暂时避避风头，否则岂非反而等于救了李寻欢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "百晓生",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "text": "不错，梅花盗此番出现，无异是在为李寻欢洗刷罪名，我若是梅花盗，也万万不会做这事的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "那么，你们的意见是——",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "text": "杀张胜奇的人，一定是李寻欢的同党，他假冒梅花盗之名出手，为的就是要帮李寻欢脱罪。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "百晓生",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "text": "李寻欢若真的不是梅花盗，他的同党也就不必这么做了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今日在菩提院当值的是谁？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "text": "是二师兄座下的一茵和一尘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "传他们进来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_yi_yin",
      "text": "五师叔的晚膳你们已送去了么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "一茵",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "text": "送去了，可是……可是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_yi_yin",
      "text": "可是怎样？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "一茵",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "text": "弟子们按照前两天的规矩，还是将膳食放在门口，分量也和昨天的一样，比平时膳食加了一倍，还有一盂清水。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_chen",
      "speaker_name": "一尘",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "text": "食盘是弟子亲自放到门口的，因为弟子想趁机看看屋子里的动静，谁知弟子刚走到门口，就听得李寻欢叫我快走，弟子也不敢停留，走出几步后，就瞧见李寻欢的手自门缝里伸出来，将食盘取去，谁知……谁知过了半晌，他又将一盘膳食全都抛了出来。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_yi_chen",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_chen",
      "speaker_name": "一尘",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "text": "他嫌菜不好，又没有酒，所以不肯吃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他当这是什么地方？饭馆子么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他说要吃什么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "一茵",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "text": "他……他……他居然写了张菜单，自里面抛出来，叫弟子们照着菜单子做，还说只要做错一样，他就原封退回。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "将他的菜单拿来瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_yi_yin",
      "text": "你们就照这张单子做给他吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "text": "师兄你……你怎能……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "李寻欢若不肯吃，五师弟岂非也要陪着他挨饿，他身子一向单薄，近年来更是一直缠绵病榻，我们岂能让他再受苦难折磨？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "text": "可是……可是我们这样做，那李寻欢岂非更得意了么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "我心中已有了打算，就让他多得意两天又有何妨？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "原来你是在装睡，难道故意想吓我？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你讨厌我？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 391,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "那么……这两天你为什么总是躲着我？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我……我只是怕自己控制不住。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你真好。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "有消息了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 405,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "那些和尚还不肯放他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 411
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "少林寺的作风一向最稳健，无论做什么都要先观察很久，绝不肯轻举妄动，宁可不做，也不肯做错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 413,
      "line_end": 415
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "但他们已等了六七天了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 417,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "也许他们还不肯相信杀张胜奇的人是梅花盗，因为梅花盗做案一向是连着来的，绝不会一次就罢手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 419,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "他们总有相信的时候，我一定要他们相信。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 423,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你随我来，我带你去个地方。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "去哪里？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 429,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "去找你第二个对象。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 431,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你看这招牌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 435,
      "line_end": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "这招牌又有什么特别之处？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 439,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你再看这招牌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 443
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "这些店全都是一个人开的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 457,
      "line_end": 457
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "嗯，全都是申老三开的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 459,
      "line_end": 459
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "现在我们还要到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 461,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你跟我来就知道了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 463,
      "line_end": 463
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你看，流星。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 475,
      "line_end": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你许了愿么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 477,
      "line_end": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "流星总是一眨眼就过了，没有人能来得及许愿的，除非他早已知道会有流星出现，但又有谁能知道流星会在什么时候出现？我看这全是骗人的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 479,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "就算是骗人的，但它却能使人生出许多美丽的幻想，永远带着它，一个人若能永远带着份美丽的希望，总是件好事。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 485
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我想不到你也知道这传说。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 489,
      "line_end": 489
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "这传说我很小的时候就知道了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 491,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你又想起了你的母亲？是不是她告诉你的？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "好高的墙，不知道有没有四丈。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 507,
      "line_end": 509
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "差不多了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 511,
      "line_end": 511
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你能不能掠过去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 513,
      "line_end": 513
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "世上没有人能掠过四丈高墙，但若一定要进去，还是有法子的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 515,
      "line_end": 517
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "这就是申老三的家。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 519,
      "line_end": 521
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "申老三就是我第二个下手的对象？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 523,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "附近几百里之内，绝没有其他更好的对象了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 525,
      "line_end": 525
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "但他却是个生意人。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 527,
      "line_end": 527
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我知道你不愿向生意人下手，但生意人也有好多种。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "他是哪一种？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "最不规矩的那一种。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 533,
      "line_end": 533
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你想，规矩的生意人怎会在同一个城里，同一条街上开十几家铺子，规矩的生意人家里怎会起这么高的墙。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 535,
      "line_end": 537
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "墙起得高些并没有错，铺子开得多些也不犯法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 539,
      "line_end": 539
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "墙起得高是做贼心虚，怕人报复，铺子开得多是因为他会抢。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 541,
      "line_end": 543
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "抢？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 545,
      "line_end": 545
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "申家是大族，上一代已有五房，到了这一代，堂兄堂弟一共有十六个之多，十六个兄弟开了四十多家店铺。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 547,
      "line_end": 549
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "算来每人只有三家铺子，并不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 551,
      "line_end": 551
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "但现在四十多家铺子全是申老三的了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 553,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 555,
      "line_end": 555
    }
